item.description:
Rock Paper Scissor Discord Create a New Game Users can initiate a new Rock-Paper-Scissors game with the following parameters:
/rps new &lt;player(s)&gt; &lt;amount&gt; &lt;token&gt; &lt;rounds&gt;
&lt;player(s)&gt;: Tag Discord users to specifically invite them to the game. Only tagged users can participate. number of users If a number is provided, it specifies the maximum number of players. &lt;amount&gt;: The amount to bet. &lt;token&gt;: The type of token to bet (e.g., icy, BTC, ETH).
